Funzionalità vista singola

- While click: select
- Cell state (and css) for selected
- Copy and paste (result = one row)
- Settings for filetype: file size, block number, block size and cell size
- Settings for view: binary, octet, hex, ascii, unicode ecc..
- Save notes, color schema and settings
- Create area
- Router-view keepalive
- Electron (change size)
- Electron hooks (fullscreen, refresh, hide frame and add exit button)

Funzionalità vista multipla
- Filelist and upload
- Known values (in toolbox or cell dropdown?)
- Slider for navigation
- Heatmap

Layout
- Toolbar (row or fixed column)
- Compare with nGordo grid or fix borders
- 4x textarea (file > block > area > cell)
- Colorpicker
- Test with most common block sizes

Computed layout
- Cell colors from [schema, stats, state] = [saved color, heatmap, hover/selected]
- Cell fontsize and fontfamily, from options
- Layout: odd cell number  (fix align center, fix fake border)
